Title: Indulekha Bringha Oil: Ayurvedic Solution for Healthy Scalp Skin and Hair Hair Oil(100 ml)
Description: The Revolutionary Indulekha Bringha Oil in a Brand New Selfie Bottle!Indulekha Bringha Oil, is an ayurvedic solution for modern day hair care problems like severe hair fall and dandruff. Indulekha Bringha Oil is composed of 100% natural herbs that are prepared in a base of pure virgin coconut oil, thus not only providing hair treatment but also nourishing your hair. Trusted by lakhs of people in India and across the world, Bringha oil is a phenomenon by itself. Now it comes in an intelligently designed "Selfie bottle". Oiling is made super easy by the innovative Indulekha Selfie Bottle. The unique feature of the bottle is the special attachment on its top. It`s 6cm wide and has got ten needles of 2cm length, with holes at the edges. This works as a perfect attachment to apply Indulekha Bringha Oil directly onto your scalp as it ensures that the oil is distributed evenly throughout your scalp. This will provide maximum effect without even losing a single drop of oil.HOW TO USESTEP 1Open the bottle of Indulekha Bringha Oil and make a hole of 1 mm on the inner cap.STEP 2Attach the cap with needles to the bottle of Indulekha Bringha Oil.STEP 3Comb using the special attachment to detangle hair.STEP 4Comb hair from front to back by gently squeezing the bottle. Make sure that the needles are in contact with your scalp.STEP 5In a single squeeze, the needles will release around 0.5ml to 0.8 ml of Indulekha Bringha Oil on your scalp. Repeat applying oil for at least 4- 5 times to release desired amount of oil.STEP 6Once the oil is applied, massage scalp gently using fingers.METHOD OF APPLICATION01.Selfie Bottle helps you to apply Bringha on scalp directly.02.Get it evenly distributed on scalp leaving each strand nourished!03.Give a gentle massage and relaxTips to Hair Growth & Hair CareWish to make your hair look fuller and more vibrant? Here, you`ll find some simple yet effective ways to take care of your hair! These natural tips can help your hair grow faster and longer.Cleanliness is important:A healthy scalp devoid of fungal infections like dandruff or any kind of skin disorders is essential for healthy hair growth. Lack of Scalp Hygiene is the major cause for hair fall. So it is important to keep the scalp clean to keep hair fall at bay. Keep it healthy to avoid dandruff and other skin diseases. You can go for a natural daily useable shampoo instead of one with chemicals.Consistent Care:Hair doesn`t grow overnight. It needs years of consistent, diligent care. Hair growth has certain phases that are controlled and facilitated by certain biological factors. The growth of hair depends highly on how we take care of it. It will be difficult to regain hair growth after a long period of neglect. So take care of your lovely locks.Healthy Diet:A slight change in your diet can either boost or hamper your hair growth. What you eat is important in promoting hair growth. Try to include fruits, vegetables, meat and fish into your diet. Make sure that you get enough protein in your diet as hair is primarily made of protein. If you are not consuming enough protein, your hair will look dry and brittle.Maintain a healthy lifestyle:A balanced lifestyle is essential to have a healthy and beautiful body. Life style changes have high impact on hair growth. For instance, lack of sleep and stress or severe emotional isolation can hamper hair growth. So try to keep a positive lifestyle which refers to adequate amount of food, sleep and exercise, to maximize your body's daily resources.Beware of styling damages:Don`t be obsessed with styling products. It may look fabulous on you, yet it`s not good for your hair. Chemical application causes severe damages to hair. If you often style your hair with hot tools, or you colour, bleach or perm a lot, hair`s protective outer layer is damaged. It results in hair thinning. If you want to color your hair, go for natural products like henna.Try natural remedies:Why go for expensive chemical products when you have effective, natural means to healthy hair.Massaging scalp with suitable oil is a proven method to be good for hair. It has been an essential part of hair care regime from ancient days itself.Try Indulekha Brigha Hair Care Oil instead of a normal oil. It`s enriched with the natural goodness of specific Ayurvedic herbs such as Bringha, Swethakudaja, aloe vera, Amaliki and Neem, which have been widely used for centuries to take care of hair.Try these tips and see the difference!
